{"tid":2258521,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"其實由幾時開始，買樓=支持政府？","createTime":"2020-10-26T05:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T04:42:13.000Z","uid":35870,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee27e3f5e94e4f37ff80612b048ef2dc9466d9e","tid":2258521,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T05:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有幾時開始，唔移民=支持政府？"},{"pid":"1167637e41883ab4d4a050a85c22363358615b4b","tid":2258521,"uid":87122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:14:30.000Z","msg":"哲學 tone: 視乎「攬炒」是咪全民共識咯，是的話全部人唔買樓，樓爆又攬炒多鑊。<br />\n<br />\n唔移民典解等如支持政府呢，就要啲時間再諗下至兜到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c975e14c6992dc9ddbbcfd40f5cf4ee6db8bca24","tid":2258521,"uid":33668,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:26:43.000Z","msg":"要睇大環境因素掛 因為Endorse 咗呢個社會發展模式同埋令政府喺宏觀經濟上獲利? 買樓=供應側上升 市場向上沖景=香港經濟向上行<br />\n<br />\n例如用淘寶=支持大陸?<br />\n點解唔係用淘寶=令大陸經濟走向廉價市場=經濟下行=反擊大陸<br />\n<br />\n食黃店=反擊政府??<br />\n食黃店=黃店擴充=地主租值回報上升=支持經濟/政府??"},{"pid":"865ff57cd1fdafb1e9579936bc4e5db0dc3c2bbf","tid":2258521,"uid":3179,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T09:18:17.000Z","msg":"因為窮人唔抵得 <br />\n點解你有得住私樓 我冇先？<br />\n你憑乜撚野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83301664b6a3623df1f3bc44bd73fc84ac64d50f","tid":2258521,"uid":233301,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1167637e41883ab4d4a050a85c22363358615b4b","tid":2258521,"uid":87122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T08:14:30.000Z","msg":"哲學 tone: 視乎「攬炒」是咪全民共識咯，是的話全部人唔買樓，樓爆又攬炒多鑊。<br />\n<br />\n唔移民典解等如支持政府呢，就要啲時間再諗下至兜到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:51:40.000Z","msg":"買樓即係支持政府<br />\n所以唔買樓就去租樓<br />\n<br />\n不過租樓就會變咗支持業主，由業主支持政府<br />\n所以應該瞓街<br />\n<br />\n但係只係瞓街，你依然番緊工，為GDP貢獻，都係支持政府<br />\n所以應該唔做嘢，拎綜援住公屋"},{"pid":"487e8c63f86cdd5cc421a04533be46bb332a2ac3","tid":2258521,"uid":244215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"On9概念，買樓咪買樓，移民咪移民<br />\n點解要有linkage"},{"pid":"d04ed16a9b825290f6b366765f3a237323284091","tid":2258521,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"因為政府就係用高樓價政策壓縮市民生存空間<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n某程度係另一種愚民政策<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加上香港樓市係幫大陸圈錢，大部分買得起新樓既都係新移民或者大陸人<br />\n<br />\n而家呢啲時間高價接貨同送錢比大陸佬洗冇分別"},{"pid":"6058fad3dd16b434a6be8ce81433848b169ddb4c","tid":2258521,"uid":27961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T16:10:40.000Z","msg":"鬥黃不嬲都係最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91aab7e9accd58e188527616cdfe4392793a2d1b","tid":2258521,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T20:00:07.000Z","msg":"口講乜乜乜 聽到啲妹妹濕晒<br />\n有人獨裁者上身當自己係救世主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有人就喺入邊偷雞摸魚搵食"},{"pid":"3df2385b7b36eca68c3fc20836466039e208d2cf","tid":2258521,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"一直都是。"},{"pid":"b47d79ffc0d8d3bdb75bf6bc02700a0617c0aa44","tid":2258521,"uid":198343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T04:42:13.000Z","msg":"政府重要收入：賣地，印花稅"}]}